t.sourceforge.htmlunit/htmlunit-core-js/2.70.0/src/test/java/net_sourceforge_htmlunit/htmlunit_core_js/NativeJavaObjectTest.java`\n\nCoverage paths exercised:\n\n- `Context.jsToJava(NativeArray, String[].class)` to reach `Array.newInstance(...)`.\n- `Context.jsToJava(customObject, Double.TYPE)` to reach `Class#getMethod(\"doubleValue\", ...)` and `Method#invoke(...)` in `toDouble`.\n- `ScriptableOutputStream` / `ScriptableInputStream` round-trip of a non-adapter `NativeJavaObject` to reach non-adapter serialization/deserialization and `Class.forName(...)`.\n- `ScriptableOutputStream` / `ScriptableInputStream` round-trip of a JavaAdapter-backed `NativeJavaObject` to reach adapter serialization/deserialization reflective invoke sites, with the required native-image unsupported dynamic class-loading guard.\n\nPer instruction, I did not run compilation or tests locally.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06839f67e7eb56ea016a288b50002881968e38ad5f8ba1ea42\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 649, "output": 849, "cacheRead": 53760, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 55258, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781041973880, "responseId": "resp_06839f67e7eb56ea016a288b373ea0819698078b09849e287b"}, "toolResults": []}
